{
  "stem": "17135.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 236.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every knew about them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were considered the-- the-- the-- how to say it-- the saints of the camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They was so concerned with survival, they have hundreds of people they helped, hundreds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every knew about it, and they had to-- you know, they had to die.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now-- now came the-- the danger if they find out that Leo Diament had a brother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't know that at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was in the camp a-- a branch of the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They called this the political [INAUDIBLE]-- the political department, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they had all the registration, all the names, of everybody that was in Buna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My luck was that in the same barrack that I slept, there was also a Jewish prisoner that was the chief bureaucrat in the political [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, he did all the-- the-- the-- the filing, the-- the-- the ordering, the-- the typing, the-- the-- the arranging.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he arranged that my files somehow will be misplaced, so they will not know that there is a brother, because they would automatically have assumed that I knew about it, when in fact, I didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We deliberated.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I ask him, why didn't you tell me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told me, [? how ?] [? to ?] [? be, ?] my brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you would have known, you would have been with us together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Is that what you wanted?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to save you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I did it for your sake.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now comes in-- in play again the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- the-- the-- SS [GERMAN] that was in charge of the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
